{"tid":2054973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港版國安法】英前歐洲議會議員撰文 促英為港人建「特設城市」","createTime":"2020-06-07T14:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T14:22:06.000Z","uid":8171,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"510069c5937f92341caaff029b9dccb379ec2c44","tid":2054973,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200607&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=61027130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200607%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D61027130&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=f151caf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200607%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D61027130&h=b53d931b\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200607&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=61027130</a><br />\n他說，如果中國未能容忍香港在其領土上擁有自由，那麼就由英國為港人提供空間去建立一個新的「特設城市」（charter city），並在這個「特設城市」複製香港的稅率和法律制度，讓這個城市成為向英國人及港人開放的定居點。漢南指此舉不會花費英國納稅人的金錢，香港人會把財富帶到英國，屆時港人將會促進周邊地區的經濟活動，就像現在的香港一樣。武漢肺炎疫情過後將面臨衰退，英國需要能推動經濟的一股力量。"},{"pid":"9b53e736c9a0ee383b9d14bfe036b74ef93b4a29","tid":2054973,"uid":151074,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"地價無兩萬一呎，住唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f6b1a036e043f153a885718a109c4c4d34cd3c","tid":2054973,"uid":50457,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"9b53e736c9a0ee383b9d14bfe036b74ef93b4a29","tid":2054973,"uid":151074,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:51:33.000Z","msg":"地價無兩萬一呎，住唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"有香港人，就會有炒賣，你駛驚？<br />\n<br />\n明明到時英國比左塊地，夠300萬人住，點知先頭部隊買定一堆等炒價。<br />\n<br />\n